      "rationale": "The commercial CFD solver (ANSYS Fluent 2022R2) is under formal SQA per the vendor's ISO 9001-certified development process. Internal regression suite results reviewed and archived. Required gradation 2 achieved."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
