      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2; experimental sample characterization documented in source publication.",
      "rationale": "Validation data sourced from FDA-sponsored multi-laboratory round-robin study. Sample preparation and fluid characterization documented in the original publication (Hariharan et al.). Formal test sample assessment not required at MRL 2; gradation 1 accepted."
    },
    {
